Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,RAPTOR. Real-time aerial persistent thermal object reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.12,0:00:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,MARADMIN 131/26 calls for digital tools to enhance situational\Nawareness during installation-level incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We pull from HIT-UAV — high-altitude infrared thermal imagery. 30\Nframes, 640 by 512, no data movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.23,0:00:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Heuristic blob detection finds heat signatures in under 30\Nmilliseconds. Persons, vehicles, fires, generators — classified live.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kamiwaza-deployed vision-language model reads the current frame plus\Nfive prior frames and writes a four-paragraph mission INTREP. …
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.06,0:01:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Structured JSON drops straight into a COC dispatch ticket. An E-5\Nwatchstander gets an actionable answer in under ten seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Set KAMIWAZA_BASE_URL and KAMIWAZA_API_KEY — same code, now behind the\Nwire. 100% data containment. SIPR and JWICS ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.39,0:01:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,RAPTOR. Powered by a Kamiwaza-deployed model. Deploy in hours, not\Nmonths.
